data.description: This beautifully 4 bedroom and 2 bath home! You will fall in love with the split floor plan and abundance of natural light that pours into the open concept living area, dining room, and kitchen. The designer kitchen has granite counters, new all wood cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Both bathrooms have new modern fixtures.Don't miss the opportunity to see this beautiful home!
